data.description: Are you in search of a spacious residence nestled in the scenic north side of Dupont, surrounded by picturesque enchanting trees and landscapes? Look no further! This home exudes a sense of openness at every corner, from the expansive living room and dining area to the generous galley kitchen boasting abundant storage, ample counter space, and a substantial walk-in pantry. The king-sized primary suite features a large 5-piece bath and a walk-in closet. Every room is generously proportioned, loft area presents the possibility of a fourth bedroom. Recent upgrades include a new AC, furnace, LED lighting, refrigerator, & dishwasher. The property is complete with a fenced backyard, convenient alley garage access, and a highly walkable location.
